---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import HeroText from '~/components/widgets/HeroText.astro';

const metadata = { 
  title: 'Terms of Service | Strategic Marketing Agreement | English Support',
  description: 'Detailed legal framework and service agreement for English Support Inbound Digital marketing projects.'
};
---
<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <HeroText title="Terms of Service" subtitle="Version 2.0 | Last Updated: April 2026" />
  
  <section class="px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 mx-auto lg:py-20 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-muted dark:text-slate-400">
      
      <h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">1. Introduction & Acceptance</h2>
      <p>These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your access to and use of the inbound digital marketing services provided by English Support ("The Studio," "we," "us"). By purchasing any marketing package, completing an onboarding form, or using our digital assets, you ("The Client," "you") agree to be legally bound by these Terms.</p>

      <h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">2. Detailed Description of Services</h2>
      <p>English Support specializes in the rapid deployment of high-visibility digital marketing assets. Our core services include Inbound English Welcomes, automated Reputation Review Marketings, Global Reach Hubs (Hanare), and full brand transformations or modernizations.</p>

      <h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">3. Financial Terms & The CapEx Model</h2>
      <p>English Support operates on a Capital Expenditure (CapEx) model. Our goal is to provide lifetime brand assets with one-time marketing investments. Work will not commence until payment is verified via Stripe or PayPal. Because we allocate strategic production resources and secure delivery assets immediately upon order, all payments are non-refundable once the onboarding process has begun.</p>

      <h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">4. Secure Asset Delivery & Strategic Security</h2>
      <p>Security is a core Hanei Standard. We operate a "Zero-Access" strategic model. We will never ask for your login credentials for domain registrars, email accounts, or hosting environments. To launch your marketing hub, you are responsible for updating a specific website address record in your domain settings. English Support provides full strategic assistance for this process.</p>

      <h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">5. Delivery Guarantees & Client Assets</h2>
      <p>While we promise industry-leading speeds (24-72 hours), these timelines are contingent upon Client cooperation. The 1-business-day launch promise only applies if all requested text, photos, and brand assets are received by 12:00 PM JST. The Client is responsible for the legality of all provided media.</p>

      <h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">6. Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
      <p>You retain ownership of your trademarks, logos, and original text content. English Support retains all rights to the underlying creative logic, delivery configurations, and proprietary marketing structures used to serve the digital assets. Upon final delivery, we grant you a perpetual, non-transferable license to use the resulting brand asset.</p>

      <h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">7. Limitation of Liability & Force Majeure</h2>
      <p>To the maximum extent permitted by Japanese law, English Support shall not be liable for any indirect damages or loss of profits. We are not liable for outages caused by third-party marketing platforms like Google, Instagram, or Stripe. Timelines may be suspended during events beyond our control (Force Majeure).</p>

      <h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">8. Warranty & Support</h2>
      <p>Every package includes 60 days of priority visibility support. Minor content updates are provided under our lifetime white-glove support policy. We do not guarantee specific search rankings or financial outcomes, as external market factors fluctuate.</p>

      <h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">9. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>This agreement is governed by the laws of Japan. Any legal action shall be brought exclusively in the courts of the jurisdiction where English Support maintains its primary operations.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 pt-10 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-800 text-center">
      <p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Questions regarding our terms?</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:text-accent font-black text-2xl underline decoration-2 underline-offset-8 transition-colors">Please contact us!</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
